{"title": "Candle and the Cat", "description": "\"To the memory of TROLLEY, This little story is dedicated.\"\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhen young Caro goes to stay with her Aunt and Grandfather, the seminary president, she learns to not be afraid of the dark and to \"be a candle\" by \"sharing her light\" with the help of Trolley the cat. In doing so, she is able to help others, including a reclusive invalid, renew their old friendships.\r\n - Summary by JHedrick", "duration": 6180, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "16548", "name": "Mary Finley Leonard"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/candle_and_cat_2112_librivox/candleandthecat_2112.jpg", "copyright_year": "1901", "genres": ["Animals & Nature", "Family"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "James R. Hedrick"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Ann Boulais"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Larry Wilson"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Caro And Trolley", "readers": [5872], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/candle_and_cat_2112_librivox/candleandthecat_01_leonard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 463}, {"section": 2, "title": "The Silver Candlestick", "readers": [5872], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/candle_and_cat_2112_librivox/candleandthecat_02_leonard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 524}, {"section": 3, "title": "The Gate In The Orchard", "readers": [12734], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/candle_and_cat_2112_librivox/candleandthecat_03_leonard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 400}, {"section": 4, "title": "The Grayson House", "readers": [12734], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/candle_and_cat_2112_librivox/candleandthecat_04_leonard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 424}, {"section": 5, "title": "Trolley Goes Visiting", "readers": [12734], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/candle_and_cat_2112_librivox/candleandthecat_05_leonard_64kb.mp3", "duration": 704}, {"section": 6, "title": "A Local Snow Storm", "readers":